    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 140</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> moderate enchantment <strong>CL</strong> 12th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> weapon quality; <strong>Price</strong> +4 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>This special ability can only be placed on ranged weapons or ammunition. Each time a ranged weapon or ammunition with this ability hits a creature, its magic designates the target. Allies gain a +4 morale bonus on melee attack rolls and a +6 morale bonus on melee damage rolls against the designated target for 1 round. Multiple successful shots fired at the same target do not increase the bonuses or their duration.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>instant enemy </em>(<em>Advanced Player's Guide</em>); <strong>Price</strong> -</p>",
